name: BananaClubToken
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Banana Club Token is the first part of the Mandox Ecosystem Governance. Powered by 6 Traits of the Bio Apes NFTs, Banana Club token will allow investors to vote and propose where the Treasury funds go and what they Fund. Welcome to the Banana Club, and the Mandox Ecosystem.
